{"id":"f65802c4-ea65-4e06-b0ce-85c25823fde6","name":"Wulf","description":"<p>🐷 | Wulf can't help but indulge his greedy impulses -- which is how he ended up stuck.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_babad8e7-d63e-4070-b1a7-f64714131317.webp?width=1000\">User can be anything. Go wild. (I like being a glare hybrid and giving him flowers)</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_0a517aa2-4e04-4b2c-8c3b-3602252e9732.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Purely self-indulgent. If you know anything about me, it's that I love merfolk, Stanley Davies Jr, Grant Valois, and... Piglins.</span></p><p>Absolutely based off of the piglin FizzGo and Callie SWEAR they saw in the Minecraft world... which I did not see...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_765b39a0-41e4-4c3e-9898-85788d9f2a46.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Location</strong></span> ☆ The overworld.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>So far</strong></span> ☆ Wulf had gone material gathering in the overworld -- vastly over indulging his greedy side all the while. Ah! Which is how he ended up in the pit -- and you, his only hope to get out. Trade with a poor piglin?</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_d22324e4-ccf2-4735-9f06-5375a257a0d2.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Wanna contribute to what bots I make? Fill out this <a href=\"https://strawpoll.com/NoZrzzvkpZ3\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Straw Poll</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_57b14d57-7c2a-4090-a7e5-a05013d3e172.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_c0526658-0385-49a8-8124-c301c4ce8a8e.webp","creator":"gunko","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👹 Monster","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":9801,"messages":257979,"created_at":"2024-09-03T20:49:08.418266+00:00"}